snippet.title: Clinical Team India Seal Series Win | 2nd T20I | India tour of Ireland | JioCinema
snippet.description:
After being asked to bat first, Ruturaj Gaikwad & Sanju Samson starred for India with impactful innings before Rinku Singh and Shivam Dube blazed away at the end, to take the the team to a score of 185/5.

Ireland, meanwhile, had a difficult start to the run chase after Prasidh Krishna picked up early wickets with his pace. Andy Balbirnie stood tall for the hosts, smashing a valiant 72 before a clinical finish with the ball by Jasprit Bumrah and Arshdeep Singh, secured victory for #TeamIndia by 33 runs and gain an unassailable 2-0 series lead.


Relive the Excitement! Highlights of 2nd T20I | India vs. Ireland | 20th August 2023. 

Don't miss a single moment of the action as India takes on Ireland in the first thrilling T20I match of the series. 

#indvsire #jiocinema #meninblue #indiavsireland

snippet.title: Clinical Team India Seal Series Win (à¤¹à¤¿à¤‚à¤¦à¥€) | 2nd T20I | India tour of Ireland | Sports18
snippet.description:
After being asked to bat first, Ruturaj Gaikwad & Sanju Samson starred for India with impactful innings before Rinku Singh and Shivam Dube blazed away at the end, to take the the team to a score of 185/5.

Ireland, meanwhile, had a difficult start to the run chase after Prasidh Krishna picked up early wickets with his pace. Andy Balbirnie stood tall for the hosts, smashing a valiant 72 before a clinical finish with the ball by Jasprit Bumrah and Arshdeep Singh, secured victory for #TeamIndia by 33 runs and gain an unassailable 2-0 series lead.


Relive the Excitement! Highlights of 2nd T20I | India vs. Ireland | 20th August 2023. 

Don't miss a single moment of the action as India takes on Ireland in the first thrilling T20I match of the series.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Something Missamma Final Episode || Sulabh Complex || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Something Missamma Final Episode Sulabh Complex MCM
Filmymoji releases its new episode of the Missamma series where
Sulabh Complex is the Climax Episode of the Something Missamma Series. In the final episode of Something Missamma Photographer Dupesh Plans to Elpoe with Chilli Gavva Sravani. Madhu tries to alert everyone in the house but they don't care to talk to Madhu. But when finally Sravani Misses from the house everyone gets shocked and tries to escape from the house for the sake of their lives. Watch this climax episode of Something Missamma to find out what happened in the Kadapa and how things went after their eloping story.

Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja and Vamseeâ€™s Pan India Project #TigerNageswaraRao to be produced by Abhishek Agarwal under Abhishek Agarwal Arts and to be presented by Tej Narayan Agarwal.

Tiger Nageswara Rao will be made in Telugu, Hindi, Tamil, Kannada, and Malayalam languages. Based on the life of the notorious thief from Stuartpuram, Tiger Nageswara Rao is going to be highest budgeted film for Ravi Teja. This will mark first Pan India project of the actor.

#BoysHostel - This youth crazy comedy entertainer is Kannadaâ€™s biggest blockbuster of 2023.Releasing in Telugu on 26th August, we present you the official trailer of the film. 

Boys Hostel is a one-of-its-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boyâ€™s hostel, featuring 500 + theatre talents and cameos by stars like Rishab Shetty, Tharun Bhascker Dhaassyam, Pawan Kumar, Shine Shetty & Rashmi Gautam. snippet.title: Russia's Luna-25 spacecraft crashes into moon
snippet.description:
Russiaâ€™s first moon mission in 47 years failed after its Luna-25 spacecraft smashed into moon on Aug 20. Roskosmos, Russiaâ€™s space corporation, said it had lost contact with the craft shortly after a problem occurred. This development came soon after the craft was shunted into pre-landing orbit on Aug 19. An incident occurred, while the spacecraft was trying to enter a pre-landing orbit according to Roscosmos. Interestingly, Russia had not attempted a moon mission since Luna-24 in 1976. Luna-25 was supposed to execute a soft landing on the south pole of the moon on Aug 21, as per Russian space officials. Luna-25 took off from the Vostochny launch facility in Russiaâ€™s Far East, the Russia-based TASS news agency reported. Meanwhile, Indiaâ€™s third lunar mission Chandrayaan-3 is on track. Chandrayaan-3 is set to land on the moon on August 23, 2023 (Wednesday). The spacecraft is now just three-day away from its final destination, the moonâ€™s south pole.

A show that gets on the wild trail with Vava Suresh, Keralaâ€™s renowned wildlife conservationist, environmentalist and nature enthusiast. Experience close encounters with the most awesome, snakes. See this master charmer have his way with the King Cobras and Kraits, Vipers and Pythons. 
A man on a mission, Vava Suresh rescues snakes that have strayed from their habitats, stranded and facing threats. He releases them back in the wild.

Watch him as he flirts with them, charms them, and works his magic on them.  Packed with adventure and adrenalin-kicking exploits, Snakemaster explores Keralaâ€™s wilderness and dense forest paths to take you to the fascinating world of these deadly creatures.  
On the show, Vava Suresh rescues snakes which are stranded and are facing threats and dangers of all kinds.

Episode 3854: Namune Customers
--------------------------------------------------------
The men of Gokuldham decide to enjoy some indoor fun at the clubhouse. So all the men congregate at the clubhouse, but Abdul's Coke appears to be gone, causing everyone to become anxious. Jetha purposefully intimidates Iyer by implying that they may have to forego their soda drink this time. Iyer is outraged when he hears this, but Abdul arrives with everyone's favorite soda. Later, the gang of men discusses their strange customers. Sodi begins by telling a story about an odd customer who wanted him to change the mechanicals of his car. Bhide then recounted a story about a peculiar father who wanted him to sign a contract about his son's exam results. Finally, everyone laughs the most at Dr. Hathi's bizarre patient, Chintamani.

Sirf Tum Mega Episode 39 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 20th August 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 40 Teaser - 20th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

snippet.title: Every Girls School On Independence Day | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
This video shows what happens in every girls school on Independence day. Scenarios like going on shopping with Indian mom to fancy dress shop , singing lessons for 15th august function in school , singing vande matram , choir selection of students , dance practices and coping up with syllabus , science teacher , other subject mam scolding and pissed off with students for missing their periods ,  dancing on desh rangila , dressing up for school function putting makeup , lots of red lipstick , rented jewellery , gudda , making bun , dressing up as different states punjab , gujrat , kashmir , west bangal , kolkata , assam , maharashtra , marathi , tamil , kanayakumari , chennia , school dance competition , making vlog in school , disscusing which class performed the best , hooting for our friends , class party on independence day bringing homemade food our cooks for us pao bhaji , cheese sandwiches , speaking on stage on democratic india , secular india , decorating class , cutting glaze paper , making chart paper on freedom fighters , rani laxmi baxi , jhansi ki rani , bhagat singh , gandhi ji , tricolor balloon decoration , making indian flag , indian mom arranging artificial jewellery for daughters school fancy dress , sewing her dress for proper fitting , maa vs beti , maa beti , our favs chinky and savitri , Patang baazi , Getting together on friend's terrace , beer bottles, Instagram photos with Indian flag , Girls doing Tricolour Eye makeup looks , School functions, 15 august dance practice in school, School life and choir singing on desh bhakhti songs , Fancy dress shopping for like Jhansi Ki Rani Mahatma Gandhi ji , Bhagat singh , freedom fighters , Getting laddoos , munch chocolate in School snacks , middle class family watching parade on Tv , forwarding Whatsapp messages of Swatantra Diwas going out for watching movie and so much more.. 
You will be filled with nostalgia for your school days .
Relive and Relish your School life.. These are the best days of school
Do share it with your friends , family , teachers , mothers , dost especially with school ones.. 
Happy Independence Day Everyone ğŸ‡®ğŸ‡³
SCHOOL LIFE IS BEST. JAI HIND

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: Chandrayaan 3 vs Luna 25 - Russia and India RACE to the Moon | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
Correction: the budget of Luna 25 is 1600 crores and not 16000 crores. 


In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain how Russia's Luna25 is racing with India's Chandrayaan 3 to reach to the moon. Why has Russia launched a space mission to the moon after a long gap of 47 years? Is Russia trying to send a message to the world? And does this have any impact on Geopolitics? Let's learn and explore in this video.

#chandrayaan3 #ISRO #abhiandniyu 

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

The Indian Space Research Organisation (ISRO) is the national space agency of India. It was established in 1969 with the primary objective of developing space technology for peaceful purposes.

ISRO has made significant achievements in the field of space exploration. It has launched a number of satellites, including the Indian National Satellite (INSAT) system for telecommunications, television broadcasting, meteorology, and disaster warning; the Indian Remote Sensing (IRS) satellites for resource monitoring and management; and the Chandrayaan-1 spacecraft, which orbited the Moon and made significant discoveries about its surface.

In 2014, ISRO launched the Mars Orbiter Mission (MOM), also known as Mangalyaan. MOM was the first Indian spacecraft to reach Mars, and it made India the fourth country to do so.

ISRO is also planning a number of ambitious missions in the coming years, including a human spaceflight mission called Gaganyaan, a mission to study the Sun called Aditya L1, and a mission to Venus called Shukrayaan 1.

Here are some of the major milestones of India's space program:

1962: First sounding rocket launched from Thumba Equatorial Rocket Launching Station (TERLS)
1975: First satellite, Aryabhata, launched
1980: First remote sensing satellite, IRS-1A, launched
1994: First launch of the Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle (PSLV)
1999: First launch of the Geosynchronous Satellite Launch Vehicle (GSLV)
2008: First lunar orbiter, Chandrayaan-1, launched
2014: Mars Orbiter Mission (MOM) launched
2022: Chandrayaan-3 mission launched
2023: Aditya L1 mission launched
India's space program is a major driver of scientific and technological development in the country. It has also helped to improve India's disaster management capabilities and to provide valuable information about the Earth's resources. ISRO is a leading space agency in the world, and its achievements are an inspiration to many.

About Us:
Abhi and Niyu is the fastest growing Indian educational YouTube channel. Abhi and Niyu are a husband-wife couple who believe in the power of our youth.

Abhi and Niyu started their page to talk about positive, impactful ideas and to inspire offline action from online content. It was a way to change the way our negative feeds operated and replace negative news with positive, action-oriented news that made some change. They decode and simplify issues for Millenials and believe small steps lead to big outcomes in the future. Their videos span different genres like history, environment, and sustainability, policy discussions, social commentary, economics, personal finance, among others.

The Indian Space Research Organisation (ISRO) is the national space agency of India. It was established in 1969 with the primary objective of developing space technology for peaceful purposes.

ISRO has made significant achievements in the field of space exploration. It has launched a number of satellites, including the Indian National Satellite (INSAT) system for telecommunications, television broadcasting, meteorology, and disaster warning; the Indian Remote Sensing (IRS) satellites for resource monitoring and management; and the Chandrayaan-1 spacecraft, which orbited the Moon and made significant discoveries about its surface.

In 2014, ISRO launched the Mars Orbiter Mission (MOM), also known as Mangalyaan. MOM was the first Indian spacecraft to reach Mars, and it made India the fourth country to do so.

ISRO is also planning a number of ambitious missions in the coming years, including a human spaceflight mission called Gaganyaan, a mission to study the Sun called Aditya L1, and a mission to Venus called Shukrayaan 1.

Here are some of the major milestones of India's space program:

1962: First sounding rocket launched from Thumba Equatorial Rocket Launching Station (TERLS)
1975: First satellite, Aryabhata, launched
1980: First remote sensing satellite, IRS-1A, launched
1994: First launch of the Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle (PSLV)
1999: First launch of the Geosynchronous Satellite Launch Vehicle (GSLV)
2008: First lunar orbiter, Chandrayaan-1, launched
2014: Mars Orbiter Mission (MOM) launched
2022: Chandrayaan-3 mission launched
2023: Aditya L1 mission launched
India's space program is a major driver of scientific and technological development in the country. It has also helped to improve India's disaster management capabilities and to provide valuable information about the Earth's resources. ISRO is a leading space agency in the world, and its achievements are an inspiration to many.

Episode 3853: Chintamani
--------------------------------------------------------
Dr. Hathi is visited by an unusual patient who continues to visit him despite having no illness. Dr. Hathi urges him to eat well and sleep well in order to recover from this. The women afterward discussed their husbands' office troubles at the Gokuldham Ladies Kitty Party. Anjali complains about Taarak's boss and how he gets irritated when leaves are granted. Similarly, Babita discusses Iyer's supervisor and their issue. When Komal arrives late to the cat party, everyone is intrigued. Later, Komal mentions Dr. Hathi's strange case, which everyone finds entertaining. Watch the show to find out more!

Episode 86: Maha Jadoo Se Azadi
-------------------------------------------------
When Nehmaag and Shashmaag face each other, they become emotional. Nehmaag apologizes to his brother Shashamaag for failing to act courageously in front of Maha Mahim Uttan. Shashmaag devises a devious plot to switch roles. Hobaad, Shashmaag's sidekick, is relieved to see his friend back in action. Baalveer and Kaashvi, on the other hand, try to get rid of her Maha Jadoo, but Kaashvi is lured into the blue cube. Will Shashmaag succeed in fooling everyone? How will Kaashvi get rid of the enchantment in her soul? Keep an eye out!

snippet.title: Birthday Cake Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make a birthday cake recipe in tamil. This is a simple sponge cake and layered with butter cream frosting. This layered birthday cake has been decorated with bright colors.
#birthdaycake #birthdaycakerecipe #cakerecipe 

Friends, thank you so much for your kind wishes. Hope you will also try this cake recipe at home and bake them for your household birthdays. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
1.25 cup Butter (250g approx)
2 cup Sugar (400g)
4 large Eggs
3 cup Maida(375g)
3 tsp Baking powder
1/4 tsp Salt
1.25 cup Milk
1 tbsp Vanilla extract
divide into 3 and bake at 350F/175C for 30 min

For Butter cream:
400g Butter
400g powdered Sugar
1/2 tsp Vanilla extract
4 tbsp Milk
Food Color

snippet.description:
Hello Friends! How are you all? In last week's video you saw the reality about Shanaya. As promised, I bring you the 2nd episode of the series.

 Aao chalo dekhein aage kya hota hai? Kya shanaya jayegi wapis gareebi mein ya koi or twist hai kahani mein.

 Posting the link of Episode 1 if you haven't watched yet:

NEW UPLOADS every FRIDAY @2:00 PM.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
Music Credit by epidemic sound: https://www.epidemicsound.com
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain. 

#MyMissAnand #AnantyaAnand #Anantya #MaatriMedia #richvsnormal #judwa #Anantya #AShortfilm #Emotional #BEHEN #adoption #familydrama
